commit.message: Surrogateescape as default error handler on Python 3
Added tests for object hooks and fixed string decoding for object names on 3.x
Saner Python 3 logic that does not depend on a bunch of runtime checks and improper unicode tricks.

Simplified tox.ini that uses python setup.py test instead of pytest
Port tests from py.test to unittest
Add support for dumping and loading binary byte strings
Things seem to be working pretty well on both Python 2 and Python 3.
Add tests for Python 2 and Python 3.
Added README and removed hg leftovers
Typo fixes and add ignore file.
